  "subject": "Implement ReadRequestExaminer for data job read routing",
  "commit_message": "Implement ReadRequestExaminer for data job read routing\n\n- Add ReadRequestExaminer to classify data node selectors into\n  broadcast, per-DMI, and error groups\n- Support exact id selectors resolved via AlternateIdMatcher\n  and FDN extraction from JexParser\n- Support contains(id, \"...\") selectors via new partial match\n  search on the alternate ID cache\n- Add extractContainsValue to JexParser for parsing contains\n  expressions on ManagedElement and MeContext\n- Add getCmHandleIdsByAlternateIdContaining to AlternateIdMatcher\n  for substring search across all alternate IDs\n- Wire ReadRequestExaminer into DataJobServiceImpl.readDataJob\n  returning ClassifiedSelectors\n- Update DataJobService interface return type from void to\n  ClassifiedSelectors\n- Add read endpoint to DataJobControllerForTest at\n  POST /do-not-use/dataJobs/read\n- Add tests for all new and modified components\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2889\n\nChange-Id: I4219d38e20395b502ed4c9c466cc5a8eec0a7882\nSigned-off-by: egernug <gerard.nugent@est.tech>\n",
